headline: Synchrony Empowers Women in Auto Care with $25,000 Donation
summary: Synchrony (NYSE: SYF), a premier consumer financial services company, today announced a $25,000 donation to Women in Auto Care, a community of the Auto Care Association. This contribution aligns with Synchrony's Education as an Equalizer program, and aims to support women in the automotive aftermarket industry.
